AWDD(8) System Manager's Manual AWDD(8)

NAME

awdd — Diagnostics and Usage

SYNOPSIS

awdd

DESCRIPTION

awdd is a system daemon that collects diagnostics and usage data locally for users that have opted in.

There are no configuration options to awdd, and users should not run awdd manually.

SEE ALSO

brctl(1)
